# Artifact Management: Scribe

All governance artifact operations (create, read, update, delete, query) go through the **scribe** CLI. The `.mos` DSL and `mgov` are deprecated.

```bash
scribe create --kind contract --title "..." [--scope mos] [--parent ID] [--goal "..."]
scribe show <ID> [--format json]
scribe list [--kind contract] [--scope mos] [--status active] [--format json]
scribe status <ID> <new-status>
scribe set <ID> <field> <value>
scribe delete <ID>
scribe tree <ID>
scribe serve          # MCP server over stdio
```

Database: `~/.scribe/scribe.db` (bbolt). Override with `--db <path>`.

## Mos Subsystems (still active)

The non-artifact mos subsystems remain:

| Subsystem | Binary | Status | Scope |
|---|---|---|---|
| **gate** | `mgate` | Active | Quality gates, linting, CI pipeline |
| **trace** | `mtrace` | Active | Traceability, architecture scanning, context mesh |
| **gov** | `mgov` | **DEPRECATED** | Use `scribe` instead |
| **vcs** | `mvcs` | **DEPRECATED** | .mos VCS no longer needed |
| **store** | `mstore` | **DEPRECATED** | Scribe manages its own store |

### gate (mgate) — Quality Gates

| Operation | Command |
|---|---|
| Lint | `mgate lint` |
| Lint (agent mode) | `mgate lint --agent` |
| Lint (summary) | `mgate lint --severity error --summary -v` |
| Audit | `mgate audit [--trend] [--velocity]` |
| Harness | `mgate harness run [--rule <id>]` |
| Doctor | `mgate doctor` |
| CI pipeline | `mgate ci [--fast] [--fix]` |

### trace (mtrace) — Traceability

| Operation | Command |
|---|---|
| Context mesh | `mtrace mesh <path> [--format text\|json\|mermaid]` |
| Architecture sync | `mtrace architecture sync [--path .] [--scanner auto] [--markdown] [--grouped]` |
| Survey | `mtrace survey <path>` |

## Context Mesh

Use `mtrace mesh <path>` to understand the governance context of any code package.

- **text** (default): tree view grouped by kind
- **json**: full graph with nodes and edges
- **mermaid**: subgraph diagram

## Examples

```bash
# Artifact management (scribe)
scribe create --kind contract --title "Fix the linter" --scope mos
scribe show CON-2026-287
scribe list --kind contract --scope locus --status active
scribe status CON-2026-287 complete
scribe set CON-2026-287 goal "New goal statement"
scribe tree CON-2026-999
scribe list --format json

# Traceability (mtrace)
mtrace mesh moslib/governance
mtrace architecture sync --grouped --scanner go

# Quality gates (mgate)
mgate lint --severity error --summary -v
mgate ci --fast
mgate doctor
```
